item.title: Leetcode Weekly Contest 192
item.description: Did well on the first two problems; spent multiple iterations on the third problem; got stuck for the last one. 3. Design Browser History This is a problem simulating browse history behavior. I spent too many iterations on debugging the offset computation. To improve, focus on the distinction between length and index. 4. Paint House III I found out the state definition early enough(about 5 minutes in). However got stuck for a long time on how to handle the house is already patined case.
